=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Classes_LinCongL_ex4 ===

DESCRIPTION: A very_dark gritty sound, with fm_or_inharmonic oscillator character around 721 Hz, featuring punchy attack and sustained envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, filtered with resonant_steep_rolloff character, and spectrally sparse.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: punchy
  brightness: very_dark
  crest_factor_db: sustained
  envelope_flatness: flat
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: gritty
  spectral_complexity_mean: sparse
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 721.0004
  harmonic_decay_rate: -10.1911
  harmonic_regularity: 0.5397
  pitch_clarity: 108.0043
  inharmonicity: 0.2585
  type: fm_or_inharmonic
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -13.9602
  resonance_freq: 602.9297

